description:
This mod update the stack size of many items.

here is the complete list of stack size changes : 
- Empty bucket : 1 => 5
- All blocks : 256=> 512
- All pipes : 10 => 30
- Industrial beams : 1 => 30
- All seeds : 
- Water / Oil / chemical liquids : 20 => 100 
- Potatoes : 50 => 200
- Fruits / vegetables : 10 => 50
- Seeds : 20 => 200
- SoilBag : 5 => 10

- Ember : 10 => 50
- Beewax : 10 => 50
- Slimyclam : 10 => 50
- Cotton :  20 => 100
- Corn : 10 => 50
- Circuitboard : 20 => 50
- Steak : 10 => 50
- Glowpoop: 10 => 50
- Flower : 20 => 100
- Glue : 10 => 50
some builing + decor object : 1 => 20
- Warehouse key card : 1 => 5
name: BetterStack
